event_text: As a storm rages across the beach and waves crash on the shore, m_c is tucked up in the medicine cat den, their sleep anything but restful. They keep seeing flashes of prophecy_list. They wake with a shiver, wondering what their dreams mean for the Clan.
The things they saw today, omen_list... m_c dips a paw in a rockpool, watching the tiny crawling life inside and considering what the omens foretell.
